{"pageProps":{"data":{"news_id":"611","news_catgory":"1","hot_news":"0","news_push":"","news_on_top":"1","news_title":"特斯拉盼於德國設廠 因環保問題遭抗議","news_summary":"","image_path":"","news_des":null,"news_content":"<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>最新更新：<span lang='EN-US'>2020/01/19 15:59</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>（中央社柏林<span lang='EN-US'>18</span>日綜合外電報導）美國電動車大廠特斯拉（<span lang='EN-US'>Tesla</span>）計畫在柏林郊區設立超級工廠，大約<span lang='EN-US'>250</span>名德國民眾今天到設廠地點抗議，宣稱這樣的建設將會危害區域內的水源供應和野生生物。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>特斯拉去年<span lang='EN-US'>11</span>月宣布，計畫在德國東部布蘭登堡邦（<span lang='EN-US'>Brandenburg</span>）市鎮格林海德（<span lang='EN-US'>Gr</span>&uuml;<span lang='EN-US'>nheide</span>）設立他們在歐洲的第一座工廠。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>政界、工會、產業團體都對特斯拉表示歡迎，宣稱那會為地區帶來工作機會，但因為對環境保護的憂慮，讓數百名當地人在今天走上街頭。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>抗議民眾喊著：「我們在這裡，我們要大力發聲，因為特斯拉正在竊取我們的水。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>在此之前，布蘭登堡邦水利當局<span lang='EN-US'>16</span>日警告，預定興建的特斯拉工廠，將使得「飲水供應以及工廠廢水排放，出現廣泛及嚴重的問題。」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>現年<span lang='EN-US'>27</span>歲的環保人士巴赫（<span lang='EN-US'>Anne Bach</span>）表示，特斯拉月初公布的計畫顯示，他們每小時需要超過<span lang='EN-US'>300</span>立方米的水，這將消耗光該地區在正下降的儲量。</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>巴赫說：「我不是反對特斯拉&hellip;而是衝著工廠設置地點而來；要設在保護野生生物的的森林區，這真的有必要嗎？」</span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>同時，民眾也為附近道路和村落之間的交通憂心不已，他們預期交通未來會有「巨幅」成長，他們為此表達抗議。（譯者：李晉緯<span lang='EN-US'>/</span>核稿：嚴思祺）<span lang='EN-US'>1090119</span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang='EN-US' style='font-size:14.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p><span style='font-size:16px;'><span style='mso-bidi-font-size:12.0pt;font-family:&quot;微軟正黑體&quot;,sans-serif'>資料來源<span lang='EN-US'>: https://www.cna.com.tw/news/aopl/202001190111.aspx</span></span></span></p>\n","keyword":"","news_order_id":"0","create_date":"2020-01-20","clk_count":"136"}},"__N_SSG":true}